Azure virtual linux machine as webserver

1. create azure virtual machine
	- make sure to select the inbound ports as HTTP & HTTPS

2. login via ssh 

4. sudo apache2 service install

sudo su

sudo apt update
sudo apt install apache2 -y

5.enable service while login

sudo systemctl enable apache2

6.reboot the machine

7.clone the git repo and make sure it as index.html file

cd /var/wwww/html/

git clone 

8.Take ip address and paste and go in browser 

Additional cmds: - 
check status of service
sudo systemctl status apache2

manullay start and stop as service
sudo systemctl start apache2
sudo systemctl stop apache2
